{"tid":1420210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[致所有被捕手足]怯，你就輸一世","createTime":"2019-08-06T04:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:37:15.000Z","uid":1834,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"522f8adee841b5de982d7e7ff03b9178d3ed2634","tid":1420210,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"6月9號至今香港最大武裝組織拘捕超過420個香港公民，我想同被捕嘅手足講聲加油。<br />\n<br />\n更加重要嘅係請你地唔好咁輕易畏懼政府嘅白色恐怖。基本法係有賦予我地集會、遊行、示威嘅自由。如果無被法庭發出禁制令，請你地唔好因為保釋緊而害怕，唔再出黎發夢。<br />\n<br />\n怕再被捕嘅，就算唔上最前線都可以係後邊玩幻彩詠香江。可以一邊企係後排充人數畀信心前排嘅手足一邊上網做和理非。<br />\n<br />\n各位被捕嘅手足，我地唔係condom。<br />\n我地唔會因為被捕就失去我地嘅價值<br />\n我地要再去諗清楚仲有咩可以做，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好灰心，唔好畏懼</span>。記住！我地仲未輸！我地仲未輸！我地仲未輸！<br />\n<br />\n被捕手足，絕不孤單<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08c4599ab0eddb9c3e3b08ad84d395edf7edf7a","tid":1420210,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:27:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b0d6c5a26ce110049e97b8ab4a025e3d531ade","tid":1420210,"uid":6674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"加油巴打，齊上齊落"},{"pid":"41975c1c53e7e938b070e950a4e7230868c826b2","tid":1420210,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你"},{"pid":"1778d04bf2ce4d02156220748022ecf9cd5f0178","tid":1420210,"uid":246803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ac516c0d1cef894b993aeeb628a211db973a35","tid":1420210,"uid":1834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"25b0d6c5a26ce110049e97b8ab4a025e3d531ade","tid":1420210,"uid":6674,"like":4,"dislike